  // ГўвЂќв‚¬ГўвЂќв‚¬ E-invoicing: KSA ZATCA Phase 2 (Fatoora) Гўв‚¬вЂќ same block as ProjectTransaction ГўвЂќв‚¬ГўвЂќв‚¬
  invoiceClassification    InvoiceClassification?
