// ГўвЂќв‚¬ГўвЂќв‚¬ Universal Travel Identity Гўв‚¬вЂќ primary source for travel & immigration docs ГўвЂќв‚¬ГўвЂќв‚¬
// Shared by Talent, Accompanying Persons, Crew, Consultants and VIP Guests.
model TravelerProfile {
  id         String             @id @default(cuid())
  personType TravelerPersonType @default(TALENT)

  fullName           String // display name
  legalName          String? // full legal name as per passport
  preferredName      String?
  gender             String?
  email              String?
  phone              String?
  nationality        String?
  countryOfResidence String?

  /// @PII
  passportNumber       String?
  passportPlaceOfIssue String?
  passportIssueDate    DateTime?
  passportExpiry       DateTime?
  /// @PII
  dateOfBirth          DateTime?
  /// @PII
  nationalId           String?

  // Photos (airport pickup, hotel check-in, accreditation, meet & greet).
  headshotUrl          String?
  passportPhotoUrl     String?
  additionalIdPhotoUrl String?

  // Passport uploads.
  passportFrontUrl      String?
  passportInfoUrl       String?
  passportAdditionalUrl String?
  passportPdfUrl        String?

  // Travel preferences + emergency contact.
  travelPrefs           Json? // { seat, meal, hotel, airline, perDiemNotes }
  emergencyContactName  String?
  emergencyContactPhone String?

  // ГўвЂќв‚¬ГўвЂќв‚¬ Travel Requirement Engine (SYS-10 V2.0 Г‚В§2) Гўв‚¬вЂќ system-calculated ГўвЂќв‚¬ГўвЂќв‚¬
  homeCountry             String?
  homeCity                String?
  workRegion              String? // shoot region for the current engagement
  isLocalTalent           Boolean @default(false)
  travelRequired          Boolean @default(false)
  visaRequired            Boolean @default(false)
  accommodationRequired   Boolean @default(false)
  groundTransportRequired Boolean @default(false)

  gdprConsent Boolean   @default(false)
  consentAt   DateTime?
  notes       String?

  // Links to the other masters (1:1).
  crewMemberId String?     @unique
  crewMember   CrewMember? @relation(fields: [crewMemberId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)

  talentProfileId String?              @unique
  talentProfile   GlobalTalentProfile? @relation("TalentTravelIdentity", fields: [talentProfileId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)

  // Accompanying persons = full linked identities (self-relation), not text fields.
  accompaniesId String?
  accompanies   TravelerProfile?  @relation("AccompanyingPersons", fields: [accompaniesId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  companions    TravelerProfile[] @relation("AccompanyingPersons")
  relationship  String? // Spouse | Personal Assistant | Hair Stylist | Гўв‚¬В¦

  trips                    Trip[]
  visas                    VisaApplication[]
  travelerVisas            TravelerVisa[]
  documents                TravelerDocument[]
  arrivals                 TravelArrival[]
  accommodationAssignments AccommodationAssignment[]
  transportPassengers      TransportPassenger[]
  shuttleRiders            ShuttleRider[]

  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  @@index([personType])
  @@index([accompaniesId])
  @@map("traveler_profiles")
}

enum TravelerPersonType {
  TALENT
  ACCOMPANYING
  CREW
  CONSULTANT
  VIP
}

enum TravelerVisaStatus {
  NOT_REQUIRED
  REQUIRED
  IN_PROGRESS
  SUBMITTED
  APPROVED
  REJECTED
}

enum TravelerDocType {
  PASSPORT
  VISA
  NATIONAL_ID
  EMIRATES_ID
  DRIVERS_LICENSE
  RESIDENCE_PERMIT
  ENTRY_PERMIT
  VACCINATION
  INSURANCE
  FLIGHT_ITINERARY
  HOTEL_VOUCHER
  INVITATION_LETTER
  WORK_PERMIT
  PERMIT_APPROVAL
  CUSTOMS
  OTHER
}

// Standing person-level visa / residence permit (distinct from the trip-driven VisaApplication).
model TravelerVisa {
  id         String          @id @default(cuid())
  travelerId String
  traveler   TravelerProfile @relation(fields: [travelerId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  visaType       String?
  country        String?
  issueDate      DateTime?
  expiryDate     DateTime?
  entriesAllowed String? // SINGLE | DOUBLE | MULTIPLE
  sponsor        String?
  status         TravelerVisaStatus @default(REQUIRED)

  visaCopyUrl        String?
  evisaPdfUrl        String?
  entryPermitUrl     String?
  residencePermitUrl String?
  notes              String?

  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  @@index([travelerId])
  @@map("traveler_visas")
}

// Typed travel-documents repository per person.
model TravelerDocument {
  id         String          @id @default(cuid())
  travelerId String
  traveler   TravelerProfile @relation(fields: [travelerId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  type         TravelerDocType @default(OTHER)
  label        String?
  fileUrl      String
  expiryDate   DateTime?
  notes        String?
  uploadedById String?

  createdAt DateTime @default(now())

  @@index([travelerId, type])
  @@map("traveler_documents")
}

// Airport Meet & Greet Гўв‚¬вЂќ arrival info per traveller (drives the Arrival Photo Sheet).
enum ArrivalStatus {
  SCHEDULED
  LANDED
  COLLECTED
  CHECKED_IN
  COMPLETED
  NO_SHOW
  CANCELLED
}

model TravelArrival {
  id         String          @id @default(cuid())
  travelerId String
  traveler   TravelerProfile @relation(fields: [travelerId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  tripId     String?
  trip       Trip?           @relation(fields: [tripId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)

  // SYS-12.F Гўв‚¬вЂќ project scoping + real-time arrival operations
  projectId String?
  project   ProductionProject? @relation(fields: [projectId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)

  airport             String?
  flightNumber        String?
  arrivalTime         DateTime? // scheduled
  terminal            String?
  driverAssigned      String? // legacy free-text (kept)
  coordinatorAssigned String?
  notes               String?

  // Structured logistics links (reuse SYS-12.C)
  status            ArrivalStatus     @default(SCHEDULED)
  vehicleId         String?
  vehicle           TransportVehicle? @relation(fields: [vehicleId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)
  transportDriverId String?
  transportDriver   TransportDriver?  @relation(fields: [transportDriverId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)
  meetGreetRep      String?
  arrivalPhotoUrl   String?

  // Real-time timeline stamps
  landedAt    DateTime?
  collectedAt DateTime?
  checkedInAt DateTime?

  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  @@index([travelerId])
  @@index([projectId, arrivalTime])
  @@map("travel_arrivals")
}

model Trip {
  id        String             @id @default(cuid())
  // Nullable ГўвЂ вЂ™ standalone trips (no project) post to the House/Corporate ledger.
  projectId String?
  project   ProductionProject? @relation(fields: [projectId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  travelerId String
  traveler   TravelerProfile @relation(fields: [travelerId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  purpose              String?
  origin               String?
  destination          String?
  destinationGeoNodeId String?
  departDate           DateTime?
  returnDate           DateTime?
  estimatedCost        Decimal?   @db.Decimal(14, 2)
  currency             Currency   @default(AED)
  status               TripStatus @default(REQUESTED)

  requestedById String?
  approvedById  String?
  approvedAt    DateTime?
  notes         String?

  itineraries Itinerary[]
  visas       VisaApplication[]
  arrivals    TravelArrival[]

  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  @@index([projectId, status])
  @@map("trips")
}

model Itinerary {
  id     String @id @default(cuid())
  tripId String
  trip   Trip   @relation(fields: [tripId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  startDate DateTime?
  endDate   DateTime?
  currency  Currency            @default(AED)
  totalCost Decimal?            @db.Decimal(14, 2)
  status    TravelBookingStatus @default(DRAFT)

  purchaseOrderId String?        @unique
  purchaseOrder   PurchaseOrder? @relation(fields: [purchaseOrderId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)
  postedTxnId     String?

  flights FlightBooking[]
  hotels  HotelBooking[]
  cars    CarBooking[]

  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  @@index([tripId])
  @@map("itineraries")
}

model FlightBooking {
  id          String    @id @default(cuid())
  itineraryId String
  itinerary   Itinerary @relation(fields: [itineraryId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  carrier       String?
  flightNumber  String?
  departAirport String?
  arriveAirport String?
  departureTime DateTime?
  arrivalTime   DateTime?
  cabinClass    String?
  fare          Decimal?            @db.Decimal(12, 2)
  currency      Currency            @default(AED)
  pnr           String?
  status        TravelBookingStatus @default(CONFIRMED)

  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  @@index([itineraryId])
  @@map("flight_bookings")
}

model HotelBooking {
  id          String    @id @default(cuid())
  itineraryId String
  itinerary   Itinerary @relation(fields: [itineraryId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  hotelName          String?
  roomType           String?
  checkIn            DateTime?
  checkOut           DateTime?
  nightlyRate        Decimal?            @db.Decimal(12, 2)
  totalRate          Decimal?            @db.Decimal(12, 2)
  currency           Currency            @default(AED)
  confirmationNumber String?
  status             TravelBookingStatus @default(CONFIRMED)

  accommodationAssignment AccommodationAssignment?

  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  @@index([itineraryId])
  @@map("hotel_bookings")
}

model CarBooking {
  id          String    @id @default(cuid())
  itineraryId String
  itinerary   Itinerary @relation(fields: [itineraryId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  vendor             String?
  carType            String?
  startTime          DateTime?
  endTime            DateTime?
  rate               Decimal?            @db.Decimal(12, 2)
  currency           Currency            @default(AED)
  confirmationNumber String?
  status             TravelBookingStatus @default(CONFIRMED)

  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  @@index([itineraryId])
  @@map("car_bookings")
}

model VisaApplication {
  id         String          @id @default(cuid())
  travelerId String
  traveler   TravelerProfile @relation(fields: [travelerId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  tripId     String?
  trip       Trip?           @relation(fields: [tripId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)

  country              String
  destinationGeoNodeId String?
  visaType             VisaType   @default(OTHER)
  status               VisaStatus @default(REQUIRED)
  slaDays              Int?
  requiredDocuments    Json?
  notes                String?

  submittedAt        DateTime?
  expectedDecisionAt DateTime?
  decisionAt         DateTime?
  expiryAt           DateTime?

  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  @@index([tripId])
  @@index([status])
  @@map("visa_applications")
}

model TravelSupplier {
  id           String             @id @default(cuid())
  name         String
  type         TravelSupplierType @default(OTHER)
  contactEmail String?
  contactPhone String?
  notes        String?
  isActive     Boolean            @default(true)
  createdAt    DateTime           @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime           @updatedAt

